1
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,119
Here, Mui.

2
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,280
She's in trouble.

3
00:00:59,799 --> 00:01:01,600
Let her settle down here for a while, Mom.

4
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:03,119
Our house is not a charity!

5
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,079
I won't take anyone in.

6
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:06,840
I'll take care of you from now on.

7
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:08,239
I promise.

8
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,040
If you're in a pickle,

9
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:12,680
take this card, and tell him Tep sent you.

10
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,239
I need to conduct a search.

11
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,200
Take him to the station.

12
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,079
Mui!

13
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,159
Muifei.

14
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:22,799
For your boyfriend's case, we need lots of money.

15
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:26,120
What do I have to do to get lots of money?

16
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,560
Sir...

17
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:44,840
Hello.

18
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,359
This is Kat.

19
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,359
Lovely Kat.

20
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:53,599
You're here early, boss.

21
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,000
New girl?

22
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,879
I'm a key partner of this bar.

23
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,479
You see all those girls?

24
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:15,800
Their job is to keep the customers happy.

25
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:18,879
Make them drinks and look after them.

26
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:22,919
Do everything to make sure they're happy.

27
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,319
This is what I want you to do.

28
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,000
The tip alone

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,840
is thousand a day.

30
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:41,080
And with those loaded folks,

31
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,439
on a good day,

32
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,960
you'll get many thousands.

33
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,680
Can I not do that?

34
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,719
Do you really want to help Poom?

35
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:59,319
Yeah?

36
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:05,240
All you have to do is let them get a little handsy

37
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:08,280
for loads of money.

38
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,159
I'm sorry, sir.

39
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,280
I'm sorry.

40
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,680
Go clean yourself up.

41
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,560
Easy there.

42
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:11,520
I thought you'd do anything

43
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,120
for Poom?

44
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,839
I'm forever grateful.

45
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,920
I promise I'll repay you someday.

46
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,959
Go back to her!

47
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
Be the vessel.

48
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,160
Those who betrays the Great Mother,

49
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:48,000
their punishment is death.

50
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,879
What's wrong?

51
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,160
The boss wants you.

52
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:57,560
Are you nuts? The boss wants you, hurry.

53
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,360
Oh, my dear.

54
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:40,839
Let's get a good look in the mirror.

55
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,519
Look at that, you see?

56
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,759
You're gorgeous. See?

57
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,000
Just a bit of touch up and you're glowing even more.

58
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:50,519
Do you have any idea how beautiful you are?

59
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,199
A beauty like you...

60
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,959
could easily be the star attraction.

61
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,040
Do you know that?

62
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:57,079
Don't forget what I told you...

63
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:59,759
Sweet talk a little bit.

64
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:01,120
"Yes, sir. Please, sir."

65
00:06:01,279 --> 00:06:04,040
And those horny bastards will give you everything.

66
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,000
Let me see your dress.

67
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,480
Perfect figure.

68
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,399
You're all beautiful, my dear.

69
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,560
A showstopper.

70
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:15,079
Good lord!

71
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,160
What's this?

72
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,399
What happened to your back?

73
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,279
It's alright, Mui.

74
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:28,120
Let me, uh..., uh...

75
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,439
Let's get her covered up.

76
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,279
Don't be scared. It's alright.

77
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,120
Chin up. I'll be right back.

78
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,240
Just a sec, dear.

79
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,160
What's wrong? You saw a ghost?

80
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,480
Are you drunk?

81
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,399
You have to take care of the customers. Don't get drunk.

82
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:48,000
The boss here is rich.

83
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:51,279
You take good care of him and you're set.

84
00:07:51,319 --> 00:07:52,800
Trust me. Go, dear.

85
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:55,399
Hello, sir.

86
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,959
This is Mui. She's brand new.

87
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,959
Go on. Sit next to him.

88
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,360
Be good to him, yeah?

89
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,519
I'll leave her to you.

90
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,519
No worries.

91
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,079
I won't bother you.

92
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,079
Hey, dear.

93
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:22,720
So you're new here?

94
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,920
Beautiful hair.

95
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,080
What happened to your back?

96
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:46,360
No need to be shy or hide it.

97
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:49,320
I like it this way.

98
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,240
It's fine.

99
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:59,039
Have a drink with me.

100
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,480
Do you want the money?

101
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,519
Take it.

102
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,840
And drink.

103
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,720
Bottoms up, alright?

104
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,159
Every last drop.

105
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,559
What kind of training did you give her?

106
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,240
She's stiff as a board.

107
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,679
I taught her everything.

108
00:10:20,759 --> 00:10:22,639
The entire textbook inside out.

109
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,759
But the girl is...

110
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:27,519
She isn't made for this. I gave her everything.

111
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:30,679
You know how naive these fresh ones are.

112
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:34,159
They're protective by nature.

113
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,360
But it's you job.

114
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:41,240
Do everything to get her working.

115
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,720
Come on, girl.

116
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:03,840
Come a little bit close, dear.

117
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,919
Hey!

118
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:06,720
What the hell?

119
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,960
Huh!?

120
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,320
You're acting all mighty!

121
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,720
Here!

122
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,320
I have the money!

123
00:11:12,519 --> 00:11:13,759
Do you want it?

124
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,840
Sir....

125
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,679
Sir.

126
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:26,120
You want my money, but you're still playing games?

127
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:27,759
I can't touch you at all?

128
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,799
Sir. - Huh?

129
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,320
You think you're such a stunner?

130
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,720
Boss, she's all scared.

131
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,279
I'm pissed.

132
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,159
She's new.

133
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:39,720
Calm down, sir.

134
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:44,840
I'll bring you a professional to keep you company.

135
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,399
Trust me.

136
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,399
Have a seat, sir. Pretty please.

137
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,919
I wish what happened to you on those hills

138
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,840
was just a lie.

139
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,639
You and your mother

140
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:15,919
shouldn't have to suffer like this.

141
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:20,639
Mui...

142
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:22,080
Why didn't you tell me

143
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,559
...that you were hurt by those terrible men?

144
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:29,320
If I had known,

145
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:33,120
I never would've dragged you into this job.

146
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,279
I'm sorry

147
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:45,399
for putting you through this.

148
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,559
You're not cut out for this job.

149
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,639
But if I don't do it,

150
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:09,559
where'd I get the money?

151
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:17,159
That's true.

152
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,279
But I mean it.

153
00:13:21,919 --> 00:13:23,759
you're not right for this.

154
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,559
You can stop.

155
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:28,960
Mui...

156
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:35,440
The customers come to my bar to unwind,

157
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:38,960
to have a good time with beautiful girls.

158
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,519
If you can’t give them what they're paying for,

159
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:48,039
then this job just isn't for you.

160
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:09,879
Can I....

161
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:21,039
do this until I can get Poom out?

162
00:15:22,559 --> 00:15:24,879
Eat this so it'll numb you headache.

163
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,799
Damn you, Mui.

164
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:49,159
You're a lightweight and you drank it all up?

165
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,120
This vial here...

166
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,480
will cure your headache

167
00:16:45,039 --> 00:16:47,320
and rid you from all the bad memories.

168
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,440
Come.

169
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:01,879
Give me your arm.

170
00:17:03,039 --> 00:17:05,960
Mui, there's nothing to be scared of.

171
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:06,960
Come on.

172
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:10,319
Be still. Be Still.

173
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:13,640
Be still. Be Still.

174
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,119
Be still. Alright?

175
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,279
No. Please no.

176
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:24,240
Mui...

177
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:27,079
Look at me.

178
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:31,599
Good. Good girl.

179
00:17:42,359 --> 00:17:43,440
That's good.

180
00:17:43,559 --> 00:17:45,880
Good girl.

181
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,759
Mui, listen....

182
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:56,400
Relax and go back to work.

183
00:17:58,039 --> 00:17:59,640
Keep the customers happy.

184
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,599
Do not cross them.

185
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:06,559
Whatever they want to do, you just let them do it.

186
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:10,240
If they're happy,

187
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:13,480
you'll get the money,

188
00:18:14,119 --> 00:18:15,920
and then you can save Poom.

189
00:18:17,039 --> 00:18:18,119
Sounds good?

190
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:16,119
Keep that hidden. Don't let anyone see it.

191
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,599
You really want to visit Poom?

192
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:34,680
Why don't you wait until you have saved more money?

193
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:40,000
I want him to know

194
00:19:41,279 --> 00:19:42,680
that I'm saving up to get him out.

195
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:47,319
Ok. I'll take you.

196
00:19:48,799 --> 00:19:49,920
He'll be happy

197
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,359
to see you.

198
00:19:55,759 --> 00:19:58,119
Mui...

199
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,920
Mui...

200
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,880
Mui...

201
00:20:02,319 --> 00:20:03,119
Mui...

202
00:20:06,079 --> 00:20:07,720
What's wrong, Aunt Kim?

203
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,640
Mui...

204
00:20:10,039 --> 00:20:11,440
Come in.

205
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:19,039
What's wrong?

206
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:22,119
Mui...

207
00:20:24,359 --> 00:20:26,200
Your mother is dead.

208
00:20:32,799 --> 00:20:35,160
Zihan was sick for a while.

209
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,720
She didn't want to worry you.

210
00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:42,400
Zihan is in heaven now, Mui.

211
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:55,119
Why didn't you tell me?

212
00:20:55,319 --> 00:20:56,480
Huh?

213
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,319
Mui...

214
00:21:04,759 --> 00:21:06,680
This isn't real.

215
00:21:19,279 --> 00:21:22,119
Why didn't you tell me, auntie?

216
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:36,039
I've made a request for visitation already.

217
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:39,960
Mui...

218
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:43,799
About you mother...keep that to yourself.

219
00:21:45,319 --> 00:21:46,880
Don't let him see you cry.

220
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:49,039
Or you'll make him worried.

221
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:51,400
Yeah?

222
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:25,079
How are you?

223
00:22:31,039 --> 00:22:33,400
Are you doing fine in there?

224
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:46,599
I made you food. There's dessert as well.

225
00:22:54,079 --> 00:22:55,599
What are you doing now?

226
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,559
Why is it?

227
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,200
You couldn't tell me?

228
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,519
You think I didn't know

229
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:19,160
what you've been doing?

230
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:24,359
Why did you let those creeps paw at you at that bar?

231
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:36,599
I didn't mean to.

232
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:43,200
It's not like I want to.

233
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,160
I don't want to do it at all.

234
00:23:52,079 --> 00:23:54,000
There's such thing as dignity, Mui.

235
00:23:56,319 --> 00:23:58,279
The reason I brought you down from the hills

236
00:23:58,480 --> 00:24:00,640
away from those savages,

237
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:05,200
because I wanted to reclaim your dignity as a person.

238
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:11,640
I never...

239
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,160
I never thought about digity at all.

240
00:24:14,279 --> 00:24:16,559
The only thing on my mind was

241
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,799
how can I get you out.

242
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:22,960
I'd do anything to get you out.

243
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:30,640
I just want to repay you for saving me.

244
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,279
I'm sorry.

245
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,720
I'm sorry.

246
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,680
It's my fault, Mui.

247
00:24:48,039 --> 00:24:50,440
I was struggling to survive,

248
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:54,559
doing illegal job.

249
00:24:57,400 --> 00:25:00,559
Forcing you to do this job in the end.

250
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,519
It was my fault.

251
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:13,240
I have never thought of it that way.

252
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:18,119
I have never thought of it that way. Truly.

253
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:25,039
I just wanted to help.

254
00:25:25,839 --> 00:25:27,400
I just want...

255
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,680
you out here by my side.

256
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,960
Together?

257
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:39,119
Do you seriously think that we should be together?

258
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:42,960
You should leave.

259
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,599
And don't you ever come back.

260
00:25:52,319 --> 00:25:54,599
You don't want to be with me anymore?

261
00:26:16,079 --> 00:26:17,720
Leave, Mui.

262
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:23,039
Don't let me see you ever again.

263
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:31,920
Why would you say that?

264
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:34,480
Why would you say that?

265
00:26:35,559 --> 00:26:37,079
I said leave, Mui!

266
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:43,599
Time's up, girl.

267
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,920
Can I....

268
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:57,400
Can I leave the food for him here?

269
00:26:57,839 --> 00:26:58,839
No.

270
00:26:59,279 --> 00:27:00,559
Visitation is over.

271
00:27:02,279 --> 00:27:03,519
Time to go.

272
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:27,279
You are a heartless piece of shit.

273
00:27:28,279 --> 00:27:30,319
You didn't even think about comforting her?!

274
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:36,640
Comfort her for what?

275
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,880
Didn't she tell you that her mom just died?

276
00:27:41,079 --> 00:27:44,759
She's saving every penny to get you out.

277
00:27:45,319 --> 00:27:47,839
She missed her chance to take care of her mother.

278
00:27:48,279 --> 00:27:49,759
Have you no shame?

279
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:54,599
That prick shouldn't have told you about her job.

280
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:14,400
F...!

281
00:28:36,839 --> 00:28:38,799
Mui...

282
00:28:41,759 --> 00:28:43,440
What's wrong?

283
00:28:49,839 --> 00:28:51,559
Hey...

284
00:28:53,279 --> 00:28:55,000
It's fine.

285
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,839
You still have me.

286
00:30:04,839 --> 00:30:06,400
How are you?

287
00:30:09,279 --> 00:30:10,680
Are you okay?

288
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:19,680
My head hurts.

289
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,640
Mui...

290
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,720
If you keep living here,

291
00:30:44,839 --> 00:30:47,240
you memories with Poom

292
00:30:47,519 --> 00:30:49,319
won't go away.

293
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,880
How about this?

294
00:31:00,519 --> 00:31:01,680
Move in with me.

295
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:10,400
Now,

296
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,839
you have no one left.

297
00:31:16,079 --> 00:31:17,839
I want to take care of you, Mui.

298
00:31:32,039 --> 00:31:33,839
You haven't got a clue

299
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:37,359
why I want to help you?

300
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,720
Despite the fact that,

301
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:43,079
you have love in your life?

302
00:31:46,119 --> 00:31:47,160
It's because

303
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:51,039
I love you, Mui.

304
00:31:51,839 --> 00:31:52,920
I love you.

305
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:01,000
You really do?

306
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,720
Mui...

307
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,920
You don't have to believe me just yet.

308
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:17,559
But I am you to see things that I'll do for you.

309
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,880
Okay?

310
00:32:29,039 --> 00:32:30,279
Does you head hurt bad?

311
00:32:37,599 --> 00:32:39,480
You wanna go lie down?

312
00:32:50,279 --> 00:32:51,359
Careful.

313
00:32:51,799 --> 00:32:52,920
Give me a sec.

314
00:33:42,039 --> 00:33:43,480
Relax.

315
00:33:44,799 --> 00:33:46,200
Don't think.

316
00:33:47,279 --> 00:33:49,319
Do not worry about anything.

317
00:33:59,759 --> 00:34:01,039
Better?

318
00:34:25,079 --> 00:34:26,159
Mui...

319
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,840
Now...

320
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:32,519
You are dead to Poom.

321
00:34:33,119 --> 00:34:34,760
You have to forget him.

322
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:41,159
Save your love for someone who actually deserves it.

323
00:34:49,719 --> 00:34:52,159
Let me be that person, Mui.

324
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:59,559
The sky was clear earlier.

325
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,840
Has a curse fallen upon us again?

326
00:37:03,079 --> 00:37:05,800
Or has Muifei....?

327
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:55,639
Mui...Mui...What's wrong, Mui?

328
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,840
What's wrong?

329
00:38:58,000 --> 00:39:00,679
The Great Mother is here! She's coming for my head!

330
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:03,159
What Great Mother? Huh, Mui?

331
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:08,559
She's coming for my head! She's coming for me.

332
00:39:08,679 --> 00:39:12,119
She's going to kill me! / Calm down, Mui.

333
00:39:12,599 --> 00:39:14,360
Calm down, Mui.

334
00:39:15,679 --> 00:39:16,719
You're stressed.

335
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,679
You're imagining things.

336
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,440
Look.

337
00:39:21,119 --> 00:39:22,679
There's no one here.

338
00:39:27,159 --> 00:39:29,000
Listen, Mui.

339
00:39:29,639 --> 00:39:31,800
There's nothing.

340
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:33,679
Okay?

341
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:38,119
No one can hurt you from now on.

342
00:39:38,599 --> 00:39:39,519
Mui...

343
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,039
I'll take care of you.

344
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:44,760
Just be with me,

345
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,519
and work.

346
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:54,360
I don't want to go to work.

347
00:39:54,639 --> 00:39:57,280
Can I not work anymore?

348
00:39:57,599 --> 00:39:59,079
I don't want to.

349
00:39:59,559 --> 00:40:01,639
You have to do your job.

350
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:05,360
How's this?

351
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,360
I'll get you another job.

352
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:09,880
But you

353
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:12,119
got to do this job in the meantime.

354
00:40:14,159 --> 00:40:15,280
Okay?

355
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,960
What's wrong?

356
00:40:48,599 --> 00:40:51,440
You're doing the same old thing.

357
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,119
Kong...

358
00:41:05,679 --> 00:41:08,960
You like seeing me work?

359
00:41:09,239 --> 00:41:11,159
It's just a job.

360
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,000
Don't think about it.

361
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:27,760
Mui...

362
00:41:30,239 --> 00:41:32,119
I love you.

363
00:41:51,199 --> 00:41:52,320
What's wrong?

364
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:54,159
There's nothing here.

365
00:41:55,199 --> 00:41:58,159
Luojin! Luojin is here!

366
00:42:00,079 --> 00:42:01,079
Mui...

367
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:03,440
The customer is waiting, Mui.

368
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:04,800
Mui...

369
00:42:05,719 --> 00:42:08,480
Go ahead, they're waiting.

370
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,559
What's wrong?

371
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:41,960
Why are you all spooked?

372
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:54,320
What's wrong, girl?

373
00:42:54,559 --> 00:42:58,199
I'm sorry. Let me go to the bathroom real quick.

374
00:43:49,639 --> 00:43:51,960
You're back? Sit here, come on.

375
00:43:54,480 --> 00:43:55,960
Let's have a drink.

376
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:58,800
I poured a cold one for you.

377
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:41,559
What the fuck?

378
00:44:42,840 --> 00:44:44,039
What? What's on?

379
00:44:45,039 --> 00:44:46,800
Luojin. Luojin's here.

380
00:45:00,280 --> 00:45:01,280
Luojin!

381
00:45:02,239 --> 00:45:04,880
Mui has lost her virginity.

382
00:45:07,079 --> 00:45:08,280
That means...

383
00:45:09,360 --> 00:45:11,480
she was cast out as the Vessel.

384
00:45:11,679 --> 00:45:12,760
And why don't you kill her?

385
00:45:14,000 --> 00:45:15,599
I can't kill her.

386
00:45:17,159 --> 00:45:19,000
Something is shielding her.

387
00:45:43,480 --> 00:45:45,480
Have some water.

388
00:46:00,679 --> 00:46:03,239
Have some more.

389
00:46:10,559 --> 00:46:11,880
Better?

390
00:46:15,360 --> 00:46:16,360
Hey...

391
00:46:16,960 --> 00:46:19,719
I want to take you on a trip.

392
00:46:20,519 --> 00:46:22,679
You've only ever seen the mountains, right?

393
00:46:23,400 --> 00:46:25,760
Have you ever even seen the ocean?

394
00:46:26,320 --> 00:46:28,719
Can I not work at the bar anymore?

395
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:31,079
I can't take it.

396
00:46:39,440 --> 00:46:42,360
Fine, Mui. Fine.

397
00:46:44,960 --> 00:46:48,760
I don't want to force you into things you don't wanna do.

398
00:46:49,320 --> 00:46:50,599
You don't have to do it.

399
00:46:57,320 --> 00:46:59,000
I'll get you a new job.

400
00:46:59,920 --> 00:47:01,079
Sounds good?

401
00:47:16,639 --> 00:47:18,280
You got here quick, Pops.

402
00:47:43,119 --> 00:47:46,079
She's as pretty as you said.

403
00:47:47,440 --> 00:47:48,480
What a pity.

404
00:47:49,119 --> 00:47:51,400
I just done it once.

405
00:47:51,920 --> 00:47:54,039
This one here, I'm telling you, she's heavenly.

406
00:47:55,400 --> 00:47:56,559
Can you guarantee

407
00:47:57,239 --> 00:47:58,840
that there'll be no trouble if I buy her off?

408
00:47:58,960 --> 00:48:00,119
I guarantee.

409
00:48:00,800 --> 00:48:02,280
She just came down from the hills.

410
00:48:02,440 --> 00:48:03,519
She has no ID.

411
00:48:04,039 --> 00:48:05,440
Both her parents bought the farm.

412
00:48:06,679 --> 00:48:08,119
Just another illegal.

413
00:48:08,840 --> 00:48:10,119
It's the same deal, Pops.

414
00:48:11,039 --> 00:48:12,280
One more missing,

415
00:48:12,440 --> 00:48:13,239
and no one cares.

416
00:48:16,599 --> 00:48:17,679
Okay.

417
00:48:22,039 --> 00:48:23,559
Thank, Pops.

418
00:48:24,280 --> 00:48:27,599
I'll get you another good girl soon.

419
00:48:30,800 --> 00:48:32,519
Hey.

420
00:49:58,320 --> 00:50:01,519
She's Muifei. Fresh down from the hills. She's expensive.

421
00:50:01,639 --> 00:50:02,960
I'll pay whatever it takes.

422
00:50:03,079 --> 00:50:04,840
Let me go home.

423
00:50:05,000 --> 00:50:07,280
This is your new home.

424
00:50:08,079 --> 00:50:08,960
Help!

425
00:50:09,159 --> 00:50:10,840
Here, you look out for number one.

426
00:50:11,199 --> 00:50:13,920
The only person who can get you out is me.

427
00:50:14,079 --> 00:50:16,039
If any of you has the same idea to run like Ple,

428
00:50:16,239 --> 00:50:17,239
you die!

429
00:50:17,360 --> 00:50:19,000
We can't wait.

430
00:50:19,079 --> 00:50:20,119
The longer we wait,

431
00:50:20,320 --> 00:50:23,239
the Great Mother's spirit will fully fuse into her.

432
00:50:23,400 --> 00:50:25,360
She'll be harder to kill.
